Provenance: purchased 1891. Ms. inscr. on t.p.: 'M Christophori Hagenbach. Basil. 1618. Maj'. Ms. annotations.
Binding: quarter calf, marbled paper sides; spine blind stamped, g. lettering; a.e. sprinkled blue. Rebound in March 1953.

Chronica, Beschreibung und gemeine Anzeige, von aller Welt herkommen fürnämen Landen, Stande, Eigenschaften, Historien, Wesen, Manier, Sitten, an und Abgang
Compiled by Christianus Egenolff.--Preface.
Date of publication from colophon.
History, Modern 16th century. Geography Early works to 1800. References: BM STC German, 1455-1600 p.204. References: Adams C1493.
